le":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131310"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131406","id":"zettel.20260420131406","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420131311","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":14,"offset":1561},"end":{"line":37,"column":39,"offset":1586},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131311"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131406","id":"zettel.20260420131406","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":3,"offset":1665},"end":{"line":41,"column":42,"offset":1704},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":3,"offset":5386},"end":{"line":67,"column":28,"offset":5411},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131406"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","id":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":154,"column":3,"offset":9840},"end":{"line":154,"column":28,"offset":9865},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131406"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"simulasi":{"type":"header","text":"Simulasi","value":"simulasi","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":50,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"summarization-otomatis-menyelamatkan-what-bukan-why\">Summarization otomatis menyelamatkan what, bukan why<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#summarization-otomatis-menyelamatkan-what-bukan-why\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Auto compaction cenderung menjaga apa yang terjadi, tapi bukan kenapa itu terjadi.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Itu berarti tool memory otomatis bisa bikin kita percaya konteks aman, padahal reasoning sudah hilang.</p>\n<p>Ringkasan otomatis biasanya fokus pada \"what\" karena itu paling mudah diekstrak: keputusan akhir, aksi, hasil. Alasan, asumsi, dan trade-off sering disingkat atau dihilangkan karena terlalu verbose dan tidak selalu tampak eksplisit.</p>\n<h2 id=\"simulasi\">Simulasi<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#simulasi\"></a></h2>\n<p>Bayangkan sesi chat coding seperti ini:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Chat: \"Kita akan pakai BullMQ, bukan RetryQueue, karena kita butuh minimal overhead dan cross-tenant isolation.\" </li>\n<li>Chat: \"Kalau pakai RetryQueue, implementasinya akan butuh state manager tambahan dan mengganggu scaling multi-tenant.\" </li>\n<li>Chat: \"Kita setuju untuk langsung panggil BullMQ dalam service saja.\" </li>\n</ol>\n<p>Kalau tool ringkas otomatis, outputnya mungkin jadi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Keputusan: pakai BullMQ.</li>\n<li>Next step: implement retry di service.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Yang hilang:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>kenapa BullMQ? (overhead rendah, cocok multi-tenant)</li>\n<li>alasan tolak RetryQueue (state manager, scaling problem)</li>\n<li>asumsi penting (jangan buat wrapper ekstra untuk fase pertama)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Karena itu, ringkasan bisa terlihat lengkap padahal reasoning sudah lenyap. Maka nilai external memory bukan hanya menyimpan hasil, tapi juga menyimpan \"kenapa\".</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — klaim diambil dari Paragraf 9.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a> — tesis utama bahwa chat AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131311\">Kolaborasi manusia multi-hari memindahkan memori kerja ke dokumen bersama</a> — baseline kolaborasi manusia yang transfer konteks ke dokumen.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — Paragraf 9</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-collaboration (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">context-anchoring (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNo